		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Is it possible to homebrew for the DS ?</div><br />Yes. The major skills used are GBA programming and OpenGL programming.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Are there better NES emulators that are DS only (using the better resolution) ?</div>
<br />There is nesDS, which can run at the 8/7 pixel aspect ratio of an NES on an actual NTSC TV, but it lacks DPCM.

		

